OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778605560
OL,3,CRoyal family enthusiast nicknamed
OL,4,C'Union Jack Man' dies aged 91
OL,6,FA Royal Family enthusiast from Weston-
OL,7,Fsuper-Mare - known affectionately as
OL,8,F'Union Jack Man' - has died at the age
OL,9,Fof 91.
OL,11,FTerry Hutt became recognisable over
OL,12,Fthe years for wearing Union Jack
OL,13,Fpatterned outfits and accessories, and
OL,14,Fcelebrating royal births by camping
OL,15,Foutside hospitals.
OL,17,FHe once spent ten days camping outside
OL,18,FSt Mary's Hospital in London ahead of
OL,19,Fthe birth of Princess Charlotte, and
OL,20,Ftwo weeks ahead of the birth of Prince
OL,21,FGeorge.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
