CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778605560
OL,3,CRoyal family enthusiast nicknamed
OL,4,C'Union Jack Man' dies aged 91
OL,6,FSpeaking about his passions to ITV
OL,7,FWest Country in 2018, Mr Hutt said:
OL,8,F"My wife thinks I'm mad but the
OL,9,Fexcitement is fantastic".
OL,11,FAt just twelve years old, Mr Hutt
OL,12,Fattended the wedding of Princess
OL,13,FElizabeth - later Queen Elizabeth II -
OL,14,Fand Philip Mountbatten - later Duke of
OL,15,FEdinburgh - at Westminster Abbey in
OL,16,F1947.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
