PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778605560
OL,3,CRoyal family enthusiast nicknamed
OL,4,C'Union Jack Man' dies aged 91
OL,6,FWriting on a GoFundMe page set up to
OL,7,Ffundraise for the costs associated
OL,8,Fwith Mr Hutt's passing, his daughter,
OL,9,FTracey Joy, wrote: "My dad was all
OL,10,Fabout living in the moment and I
OL,11,Fstrived to provide everything he
OL,12,Fwanted and make everything happen as
OL,13,Fthe ideas entered into his mind over
OL,14,Fthe years, because as we all know,
OL,15,Ftomorrow isn't guaranteed".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
