PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778605560
OL,3,CRoyal family enthusiast nicknamed
OL,4,C'Union Jack Man' dies aged 91
OL,6,FMr Hutt had to take early retirement
OL,7,Fat 54, after having a triple heart
OL,8,Fbypass. Ms Joy told ITV West Country
OL,9,Fthat after this, her father "dedicated
OL,10,Fhis life to fighting for people's
OL,11,Frights".
OL,13,FThe Royal superfan was given 10 to 15
OL,14,Fyears to live after his heart bypass
OL,15,Fbut ended up living 37 years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
