PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778605560
OL,3,CRoyal family enthusiast nicknamed
OL,4,C'Union Jack Man' dies aged 91
OL,6,FMs Joy added that "the royal stuff"
OL,7,Fwas her father's hobby - the rest of
OL,8,Fhis time he spent campaigning for
OL,9,Fcauses close to his heart, including
OL,10,FSt Bart's Hospital, bus passes for
OL,11,Fpensioners, public toilet availability
OL,12,Fand the NHS.
OL,14,FShe described one stand-out moment in
OL,15,FMr Hutt's activism journey, when he
OL,16,Fchained himself to a bus in 1997 to
OL,17,Fpush for London Transport to make
OL,18,Fbuses wheelchair accessible.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
